{
  "stem": "12666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were definitely valid, because after World War I, many of those war criminals were put into plush German jails, and lived in luxury, and then, for good behavior, they were released.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at Nuremberg, we were trying to punish the war criminals, so that it would be a warning against other crimes that are occurring, even today.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, for example, to attack a country without a declaration of war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why the Nuremberg trial is not very popular, right, because everybody is starting a war without a declaration of war, right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just march in and make war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or, the Germans did destroy the village of Lidice in Czechoslovakia as a-- and the same method is being used today too, right?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The same method that we condemned in Nuremberg is being used today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's why I don't know what that trial in the Hague, Holland is going to face, whether they can do the-- something to stop the war crimes, because there are war crimes still occurring even today.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What was your impression of some of the American attorneys that were there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Do you have an opinion about the judges, the attorneys, your colleagues?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Can you tell me about this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, unfortunately, some of the lawyers didn't know the German history or the German background, which handicapped them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just like today we don't know too much about Bosnia, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we make a lot of errors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to know-- even American businessman are not very successful abroad because they do not know the history of the people and the-- what the people like.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I met a German salesman in Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boy, he spoke fluent Bulgarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew the Bulgarian history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he always tried to please the client.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
